## Summary
This documentation explains methods to manage invalid or erroneous data in Amplitude Data, including drop filters (query-time exclusion without permanent deletion), block filters (prevents data ingestion), blocking specific events/properties, and permanently deleting events/properties, with detailed steps for implementing each approach.

